      "updated": 1775354153191,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ast\n    - Program\n        Vec<Statement>\n    - Statement\n        let(LetStatement) => let x = 10;\n        return(ReturnStatement) => return x;\n        expression(ExpressionStatement) => x + 10 + 1;\n        blockStatement(BlockStatement) => {...}\n- Expression(可以给别人赋值)\n        InfixExpression => 5 + 3\n        PrefixExpression => -5, !ture \n        BooleanExpression => true, false\n        IfExpression =>  let x = if <condition> <expressionStatement> else <..>\n        Identfier => let x = y\n        IntegerLiteral => let x = 5;\n        FunctionLiteral => let f = fn(x) { x + 1 }; (define)\n        CallExpression =>  let x = fn(a,b)  (call)\n\n    \n\n    ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ast\n    - Program\n        Vec<Statement>\n    - Statement\n        let(LetStatement) => let x = 10;\n        return(ReturnStatement) => return x;\n        expression(ExpressionStatement) => x + 10 + 1;\n        blockStatement(BlockStatement) => {...}\n- Expression(可以给别人赋值)\n        InfixExpression => 5 + 3\n        PrefixExpression => -5, !ture \n        BooleanExpression => true, false\n        IfExpression =>  let x = if <condition> <expressionStatement> else <..>\n        Identfier => let x = y\n        IntegerLiteral => let x = 5;\n        FunctionLiteral => let f = fn(x) { x + 1 }; (define)\n        CallExpression =>  let x = fn(a,b)  (call)\n\n    \n\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
